description: Neal's On Wheels is an culinary comfort food  experience, offering delicious dishes, from smoked pulled pork so tender and juicy it melts in your mouth to BBQ ribs that are smoked to perfection. With everything fresh daily, from the succulent smoked ribs to a delightful vegetarian selection, Neal's on wheels will have what you want. So don't hesitate to stop on by and try this southern experience, or we will bring it to you!
name: Neal's On Wheels
